> So how to query to get specific Mesh pls?

I managed to do it like this, bear in mind this is for `MeshMaterial2d`, I have not experimented with the regular `MeshMaterial`, but I would assume it works the same.

```
fn custom_material_system(
    mut custom_material: ResMut<Assets<CustomMaterial>>,
    specific_mesh: Single<&MeshMaterial2d<CustomMaterial>, With<SpecificMeshComponent>>,
) {
    if let Some(material) = custom_material.get_mut(specific_mesh.0.id()) {
        // Your logic here
    }
}

```
